description: This file contains unit tests for the newsdataClient utility functions related to parameter normalization and endpoint selection within the news data fetching module.

methods.name: normalizeParams
methods.description: Normalizes input parameters for news data API requests, handling defaults, trimming, validation, and date constraints.

methods.name: chooseEndpointPath
methods.description: Determines the API endpoint path based on normalized parameters, selecting '/latest' or '/news' accordingly.
